---
title: Greek-Inspired Double Chicken and Couscous Salad with Lemon Cream
description: Dill-garlic-dusted chicken tenders seared to golden-brown perfection are paired with a couscous Greek salad in this Mediterranean-inspired meal. A finishing dollop of lemon cream adds a bright punch of flavour!
